Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I.A.2(a) | Description :The Recipient shall prepare the annual work plans and budget andfurnish to the Association not later than November 30 of each yearduring implementation of the project | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II.A.1 | Description :The Recipient shall prepare project report covering a period of onecalendar quarter and furnished to the Association not later than 55 days after end of the period | Due Date :30-Sep-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II.B.2 | Description :Recipient shall prepare and furnish to the Association no later than45 days after the end of each quarter the interim unaudited financial reports | Due Date :30-Sep-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II.B.3 | Description :Recipient shall furnish to the Association audited financialstatements covering each fiscal year not later than 6 months after theend of such period | Due Date :29-Jun-2012
